			Profile
			
			BriefIntroductionofZhengXU
（+8657187952074;xuzheng007@zju.edu.cn;www.hvdc.cn）
&nbsp;
ZhengXuwasborninZhejiang,China,inSeptember1962.HereceivedtheBS,MSandPh.D.degreesfromZhejiangUniversity,Chinain1983,1986and1993respectively,allinElectricalEngineering.HehasbeenwiththeElectricalEngineeringDepartmentofZhejiangUniversitysince1986andbecameaprofessorofZhejiangUniversityin1998.FromJune1995toJune1996hewasavisitingscholarinCanterburyUniversity,NewZealand.In1998hewasavisitingresearcherinSiemensGermany.Hehaspublishedmorethan200technicalpapersincoremagazinesofelectricalengineering.Hehasbeeninchargeofmorethan30scientificresearchprojects,including2projectssupportedbyNationalNaturalScienceFoundationofChinaand1projectsupportedbyNationalKeyBasicResearchSpecialFundofChinaand3projectssupportedbytheNationalEleventh-FiveYearResearchProgramofChina.Hehasreceivedseveralscientificawards,includingNationalNaturalScienceAwardandNationalScienceandTechnologyProgressAward.HisresearchareaincludesHVDC,FACTS,powerharmonicsandpowerquality.Hehaswritten2booksandtranslated9books.
WrittenBooks:
(1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ZhengXU.DynamicPerformanceAnalysisofAC/DCPowerSystems,PublishedbyChinaMachinePressin2004,Beijing.(InChinese)
(2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ZhengXU.GuideforPowerSystemAnalysisStudy,PublishedbyChinaMachinePressin2004,Beijing.(InChinese)
TranslatedBooks:
(1)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;EHVACUndergroundingElectricalPower&ndash;PerformanceandPlanning&rdquo;(EnglisheditionpublishedbySpringerPress,2010.TheauthorsareR.Benato,A.Paolucci.TranslatedbyZhengXu,ChineseeditionpublishedbyChinaMachinePressin2012,Beijing)
(2)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;WindEnergyGeneration&ndash;ModellingandControl&rdquo;(EnglisheditionpublishedbyWileyPress,2009.TheauthorsareOlimpoAnaya-Lara,NickJenkins,JanakaEkanayake,PhillCartwrightandMikeHughes.TranslatedbyZhengXu,ChineseeditionpublishedbyChinaMachinePressin2011,Beijing)
(3)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;PowerElectronicsinSmartElectricalEnergyNetworks&rdquo;(EnglisheditionpublishedbySpringerPress,2008.TheeditorsareR.StrzeleckiandG.Benysek.TranslatedbyZhengXu,ChineseeditionpublishedbyChinaMachinePressin2010,Beijing)
(4)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;InstantaneousPowerTheoryandApplicationstoPowerConditioning&rdquo;(EnglisheditionpublishedbyIEEEPress,2007.TheauthorsareHirofumiAkagi,EdsonHirokazuWatanabeandMauricioAredes.TranslatedbyZhengXu,ChineseeditionpublishedbyChinaMachinePressin2009,Beijing)
(5)&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&ldquo;DistributionReliabilityandPowerQuality&rdquo;(EnglisheditionpublishedbyCRCPress,2006.TheauthorisT.A.Short.TranslatedbyZhengXu,ChineseeditionpublishedbyChinaMachinePressin2008,Beijing)
